Krav Maga Weapon Defenses - The Contact Combat System of the Israel Defense Forces (2012).epub Gooner

Publisher: Ymaa Publication Center (16 July 2012)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 1594392404
ISBN-13: 978-1594392405

Israeli Krav Maga is the Israel Defense Force's official self-defense system. This system is simple, instinctive, adaptable, and effective to thwart a life threatening assault. This book presents the most up to date weapon defensive techniques that are incorporated into green, blue, brown, and black belt curriculum's. Many techniques are being revealed to the public for the first time
